reviewText:
Early Access Review

I always wanted to play a survival game which has a similar mechanic like Ultima Online, a game where you can do A LOT OF THINGS! And Zomboid offers it: Realistic Survival system, Crafting, Farming, Looting, Cooking, Hoarding, Sleeping, Timelapse, Coop... you can almost do everything and this is just an early access! I recommend this game for all survivorfans out there. Just try the demo, if you don't know much about Zomboid :)

@Update: The new splitscreen mode can handle up to 4 players! I played it with my brothers and it was just freaking amazing! The devs are trying really hard to make this game into the most realistic zombie simulation game ever made and you know what, I'm really impressed :) Keep up the good work!
